{"tid":1580483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【大陸杯葛】杜琪峯受壓終跪低 辭任金馬獎評審團主席","createTime":"2019-09-19T05:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:25:15.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c728be7dcdd1604666c0fd3c0bb55f1d9513467","tid":1580483,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190919/large/1568871325_0e48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568871325_0e48.jpg&h=70ae6941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年第55屆金馬獎得獎者導演傅榆台上感言的「台獨風波」，引發今年中國國家電影局杯葛今屆金馬獎，禁止大陸電影及藝人參加。不少香港電影商及港星亦緊跟大陸口徑，多套原本已報名的港片，亦已撤回申請，惟當時擔任本屆馬獎評審團主席的導演杜琪峯仍未表態。不過事件發展到今日，杜琪峯最終辭任主席一職，其職位將由台灣資深導演王童頂替。<br />\n<br />\n金馬執委會表示，原訂擔任第56屆金馬獎評審團主席的杜琪峯，現因與電影投資方的製作合約所限而提出請辭。杜琪峯表示，為此帶來的不便，他深感抱歉。金馬執委會以及主席李安對杜導的處境表示理解，也祝福杜導演新作順利。本屆評審團主席將由王童出任，他先後贏過7座金馬獎，包括最佳導演、美術及服裝造型獎各2座及今屆終身成就獎得主；他執導的影片亦曾三獲金馬獎最佳劇情片及一座最佳動畫長片。王童表示將會全力以赴，李安也感謝他的鼎力相助。本屆金馬獎入圍名單將於下月1日公佈，頒獎典禮於11月23日在台北舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190919/60061055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60061055&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5T11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=a0ed89af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60061055&h=fa412053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190919/60061055</a>"},{"pid":"8c6d98b51459225bfc50a6b51402274d3cb26e46","tid":1580483,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7754327b507d116903c752ee6bbe768e5e837e2b","tid":1580483,"uid":204246,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"一個深黃既導演，早期拍D有質素既本土片就個個就睇翻版，拍合拍片賺錢又比人話奶共，香港人永遠都得把口，唔會支持自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d13990c7786944202d47487d3564a03998c11b","tid":1580483,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"杜蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edc4308f5510aa2fefd8a8d925ce77367414a95","tid":1580483,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13123b700513c141711482dc5eb774ac2fa6246f","tid":1580483,"uid":101392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"唉...連杜sir都跪低<br />\n明明拍過《黑社會》串特首選舉<br />\n《以和為貴》串中共「黑社會都要愛國」<br />\n《PTU》串黑警「黑黑相衛」 <br />\n策劃《樹大招風》講主權移交後變遷<br />\n估唔到連佢都要跪"},{"pid":"dbcf63f9b1e4979f1ab2ad2157481fb09fdd25ec","tid":1580483,"uid":42982,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ff82f3e42f227bda6e333dfd0e9496bcb46b9e","tid":1580483,"uid":225130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"唔係跪既<br />\n<br />\n如果做埋護旗手就要屌啦"},{"pid":"a06c404a9c6cc99b14903cc36abad84f09c241b0","tid":1580483,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774ff79c36c03ccfed3986d2a9fdc4adb26b8393","tid":1580483,"uid":119792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"睇黎好快做護旗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}